room_title: Escape room "Foreign Agent" by Premier Escape Rooms in San Antonio
review: It was really fun, and it was hard! My father and I did the foreign agent room today, but while we didn't complete it in time, it was still a lot of fun.

room_title: Escape room "Foreign Agent" by Premier Escape Rooms in San Antonio
review: My friends and I played the Foreign Agent room! It was a blast. We will definitely be coming back to try the other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "Foreign Agent" by Premier Escape Rooms in San Antonio
review: We had an absolute blast! What a great family bonding experience as each person's talent shown through. Tammy was a wonderful hostess! We did the Foreign Agent puzzle which was medium/hard, but was great for a party of five...we will be back definitely!
